  "text": "On the other hand, greater expression levels of genes involved in IL-4 specific responses such as alterations of lipid metabolism, chemotaxis, adhesion and phagocytosis could be observed in IL-4/TNF-DC. These genes include for example ALOX15, MDC, CD209, and FCER2 [CITATION_1] . Similarly, typical TNF-α induced genes involved in intracellular signaling and transcriptional regulation like NFKBIA and EGR1 were higher expressed in IL-4/TNF-DC [CITATION_2] .",
